# World Choir — Core Rules

## No terminal for the user
The user never uses the terminal. Handle git, GitHub, Vercel, and database setup yourself.

## Real data only
Never hardcode or invent participation numbers, fake friends, seed cities, or placeholder memories.
All counts come from Supabase. Show 0 and honest empty states when no data exists.

## Auto deploy
After code changes, run `bash scripts/sync-deploy.sh "message"` before ending.

- GitHub: https://github.com/PedroSousa008/world-choir-app
- Vercel: https://world-choir-app.vercel.app
- Database: Supabase (`VITE_SUPABASE_URL`, `VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`)

## Design direction
Human, clean, universal — not luxury or glamorous. Sans-serif, warm neutrals, calm blue accents.
